messages.title: The Best for Reading West
messages.content: I've backed Victoria Groulef right from the start and it's why I'm now coming out of retirement to campaign for her to be our next Labour MP. I know that Vicky will be an MP that puts you and your family first and who will fight day and night for the best deal for her constituency irrespective of party politics.

contactInformation.address: 3 Windsor Square, Silver Street, Reading RG1 2TH
